arStrings.szText: We were negotiating with these thieving... {i}sine{/i} when we were attacked. We tried to explain that this is sacred land protected by Wasipotsu, but they refuse to listen.
sinē (seen-eh) means "trash", Wasīpotsū (pronounced Wass-E-pots-U); tone is one of Disgust
This scum got what he deserved but his accomplice got away with the artifact. It must be returned to appease Wasipotsu. If you can find them and retrieve it, we will be extremely grateful.
